snippet.title: Sega Dreamcast | Culdcept 2 | Gameplay
snippet.description: Culdcept (カルドセプト, Karudoseputo) is a turn-based strategy video game. It has drawn comparisons to other modern strategy titles, and also shares features with non-video games Monopoly and Magic: The Gathering. The first installment to reach North America was the expanded port of Culdcept Second released for the Sega Dreamcast, the North American release was simply titled Culdcept.
